text: Raj Banshi Mahto is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India from the Balia in Bihar as a member of the Rashtriya Janata Dal. ==References== ==External links== *Official biographical sketch in Parliament of India website Category:Rashtriya Janata Dal politicians Category:12th Lok Sabha members Category:Janata Dal politicians Category:Lok Sabha members from Bihar Category:1955 births Category:Living people
title: Raj Banshi Mahto
